abstract: Indy car driver James Hinchcliffe returns to track for first time since nearly fatal accident in May during practice for Indianapolis 500.
lead_paragraph: James Hinchcliffe will be back in an Indy car for the first time since a nearly fatal accident in May when he tests next week at Road America in Elkhart Lake, Wis.

headline.main: Hinchcliffe to Make Comeback From Crash
headline.print_headline: Hinchcliffe to Make Comeback From Crash
